title: "Efficient deep neural networks에 대하여"
category: "ai papers"
publishedAt: "2022-12-08"
thumbnail: "https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/79881119/209087790-826f9967-3a81-42c9-9bd3-a05f5b75485b.png"
